'''馬瑟爾堡'''（{{lang-en|'''Musselburgh'''}}，[[蘇格蘭蓋爾語|蘇格蘭蓋爾語]]：''Baile nam Feusgan''）<ref>{{cite web|title=Musseburgh|url=http://www.gaelicplacenames.org/databasedetails.php?id=1028|work=National Place-Names Gazetteer|publisher=[[Ainmean-Àite_na_h-Alba|Ainmean-Àite na h-Alba]]|accessdate=22 October 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425002224/http://www.gaelicplacenames.org/databasedetails.php?id=1028|archive-date=2012-04-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 是[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[東洛錫安|東洛錫安]]最大的市鎮，位於[[福斯灣|福斯灣]]沿岸，位於[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]東部{{convert|6|mi|km}}處。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eastlothian.gov.uk/info/476/local_history_and_heritage/558/musselburgh | title = Musselburgh | accessdate = 2012-05-29 | archive-date = 2017-06-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170622134343/http://www.eastlothian.gov.uk/info/476/local_history_and_heritage/558/musselburgh | dead-url = no }}</ref>

Musselburgh一詞來自於[[古英語|古英語]]''mussel''，意指貝類生物。<ref>Musselburgh was famous for the mussel beds which grew in the Firth of Forth; after many years of claims that the mussels were unsafe for consumption a movement has been started to re-establish the mussel beds as a commercial venture.
</ref>''burgh''則是古“鎮”的意思。<ref>http://www.gwp.enta.net/scothist.htm#places {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060517202634/http://www.gwp.enta.net/scothist.htm |date=2006-05-17 }}</ref>

其歷史可以追溯到公元80年的[[羅馬不列顛|羅馬不列顛]]時期。1975年前屬於[[中洛錫安|中洛錫安]]，據1973年蘇格蘭當地政府法案（Local Government (Scotland) Act 1973）部份劃入[[東洛錫安|東洛錫安]]，1996年劃入東洛錫安[[單一管理區|單一管理區]]。

==教育==
該地知名學校包括[[勞埃特學校|勞埃特學校]]和成立於16世紀的[[馬瑟爾堡語法學校|馬瑟爾堡語法學校]]。此外[[瑪格麗特皇后大學|瑪格麗特皇后大學]]也坐落於該地。

== 運動==
馬瑟爾堡銀箭（Musselburgh Silver Arrow）是英國最早的運動獎盃之一。<ref>Hugo Arnot, The history of Edinburgh, from the earliest accounts, to the year 1780, Edinburgh, 1816</ref> 每年由[[皇家弓箭手連|皇家弓箭手連]]成員爭奪，其歷史可追溯到1603年。

此外馬瑟爾堡也是{{le|馬瑟爾堡賽馬場|Musselburgh Racecourse}}和[[馬瑟爾堡林克斯|馬瑟爾堡林克斯]]高爾夫球場所在。<ref name="Musselburgh links">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/scotland/edinburgh_and_east/7949045.stm |title=Links play out onto record books |publisher=BBC News.co.uk |accessdate=2009-03-18 |date=2009-03-17 |archive-date=2009-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090321081222/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/scotland/edinburgh_and_east/7949045.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 此外還有叫做Musselburgh Athletic F.C.的鎮青年足球隊和叫做Musselburgh RFC的RBS錦標賽乙聯足球隊。

